MESSAGE: Hey, Abby it is almost Christmas time and I am so happy, do you know why?
So I can get presents from Santa!
Since this is the end now i wanted to say that I learned that Christmas isn't about toys and gifts it is about loving and caring about Jesus and your family.
Noooooooooooooooooooooooooooo!!!
Abby, Nooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo
Hello, Dani
Why?
That is not right, Christmas is all about your family and being with them.
Is that a fairy?
I don't want to leave yet
Noooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooooo!!!
Hello
Indeed, I am Trisha the Fairy of Christmas and I have come because I hear that one of you are saying that Christmas is only about presents that is wrong.
I am going to take you kids on a trip to see that Christmas is all about family.
Good, Dani you learned what Christmas is all about!
I'm sorry but it's too late for you guy's to stay we're already to your house.
Bye
We are about to come at your house.
You are not about to go she-hulk in my presence. Abra Ca Dab Ra
Fairy God mother here!
